{"tid":805903,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有圖港隊3項鐵人條女露毛？","createTime":"2018-09-04T08:35:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-04T13:52:02.000Z","uid":179810,"like":2,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5a00cb6664c2f0e443398a97e283e60074c79333","tid":805903,"uid":179810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T08:35:06.000Z","msg":"左邊條女係咪冇剃乾淨西毛 定只係太黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n港隊亞運三項鐵人混合接力賽得銅牌<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1415784-20180902.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1415784-20180902.htm&d=4LxgvR7ehd5k%2F1H1t1yFwzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=39391519\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1415784-20180902.htm&h=6b99b641\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1415784-20180902.htm</a><br />\n港隊在今屆三項鐵人混合接力賽奪得銅牌。（港協暨奧委會圖片）<br />\n<br />\n港隊出戰今屆亞運最後一項賽事，是三項鐵人混合接力賽，奪得銅牌。<br />\n<br />\n港隊上屆在這個項目僅得第四，今屆只有蔡欣妍仍在陣中，她與羅亮添、黃子圖以及Bailee Briana Brown出戰，以1小時33分04秒完成比賽，快第四的中國隊19秒得到銅牌。<br />\n<br />\n日本隊以1小時30分39秒得到金牌，南韓隊差超過兩分鐘得銀牌。"},{"pid":"91fc3dfa40618d648493412b9dd78d47e694a21f","tid":805903,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T08:37:01.000Z","msg":"男定女"},{"pid":"de41ce54a87e7dc04737d4e40b77cb8d3d5c36bb","tid":805903,"uid":122134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T08:42:07.000Z","msg":"做咩唔加慎入"},{"pid":"c51543097b7d6e4726ba630ffa97f231465191d3","tid":805903,"uid":204306,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T08:42:56.000Z","msg":"睇完洗眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"260a7bd9111435b89c741d2399c168e0cb7445aa","tid":805903,"uid":124020,"like":1,"dislike":